{"tid":2256124,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"逸東招手：港人毋忘空服員功勞","createTime":"2020-10-24T06:22:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T16:23:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9d7f02c9d4f08aba15a9ee29f228e46e62000814","tid":2256124,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T06:22:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201024/MNERQFRVWVE3DF3YPTQDYC2TFU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201024%2FMNERQFRVWVE3DF3YPTQDYC2TFU%2F&d=ob16Qiumsg8bXj4Ev1LzLIm5R6Uo%2BMV3ZOx7awwfaZg%3D&h=955237b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201024%2FMNERQFRVWVE3DF3YPTQDYC2TFU%2F&h=efefecb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201024/MNERQFRVWVE3DF3YPTQDYC2TFU/</a><br />\n<br />\n逸東招手：港人毋忘空服員功勞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/k8BSu_XHFiifYaLxtpw1Ijn-Kj4=/720x498/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KWN7QKZN7VHS5FHCSNIU5TTZJE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fk8BSu_XHFiifYaLxtpw1Ijn-Kj4%3D%2F720x498%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKWN7QKZN7VHS5FHCSNIU5TTZJE.jpg&h=287f392f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■逸東發文邀請被裁的國泰及港龍員工應徵其酒店職位。逸東fb圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】5,300名國泰及港龍員工失去飯碗，引起社會關注。鷹君集團旗下的香港逸東酒店昨在其facebook專頁發文，邀請被裁的國泰和港龍員工加入酒店工作，指「兩家航空公司一直以其卓越的服務和出色員工廣為人知，而我們正為銷售及市場部、酒店前台、餐廳和酒吧等招募多個職位，誠邀您加入成為Eaton HK的一分子，共同為這個地方提供最優質的服務」。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：黃楚標：大灣區航空力爭港龍航權<br />\n<br />\n帖文表示，國泰航空早前公佈企業重組消息，對香港以及所有受影響的員工都經歷最艱難的時刻。對於那些失去工作的員工、航空業和香港都感到相當惋惜。同時，逸東感謝他們作為香港的全球大使，一直為大家付出的努力，港人不會忘記。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃店盼支援同路人<br />\n<br />\n香港中小企食店聯盟召集人林瑞華昨日亦在其fb專頁發文，以「逆境同行」為題，「面對疫情下的困境，我們不忘齊上齊落的精神」，連日來有黃店老闆向他表示仍有少量空缺可以增聘人手，希望支援更多同路人。林指雖然飲食界的空缺不算多，但仍希望略盡綿力；招聘廣告更寫上「國泰港龍員工優先考慮」，有興趣者可將履歷傳送至2020smrf@gmail.com。"},{"pid":"baac7b7fcf5bb5774ed5387c6d642c92e1da05d5","tid":2256124,"uid":162567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T06:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7919d661d732dea5379ec69661c16e1fd5e50a0d","tid":2256124,"uid":95059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T06:24:06.000Z","msg":"做返飲食業本行 專業麻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cf5858ce0e3d1c10adac835ceb0994bdbc1b7ff","tid":2256124,"uid":344625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T06:25:20.000Z","msg":"一條龍服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7d851bcc0f36dfb765fbf0268bb29a0d650ec5","tid":2256124,"uid":310817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T07:09:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c922128e2ef318e6d8ffb80677b03b1b42b0dc7","tid":2256124,"uid":63400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T08:08:01.000Z","msg":"譚仔阿姐：大家都是中國香港的侍應生，只是飛天/走地的不同"},{"pid":"d12f231ff3888406044f97160ebe9b9814095b7e","tid":2256124,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T16:18:38.000Z","msg":"羅寶憐反trump"},{"pid":"09e4939d55cf7f34986a144a0ed2ab56e4d18cf4","tid":2256124,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d12f231ff3888406044f97160ebe9b9814095b7e","tid":2256124,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T16:18:38.000Z","msg":"羅寶憐反trump"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T16:22:24.000Z","msg":"Anti trump =/= 敵人"},{"pid":"857d1